Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.99,0:23:56.66,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}Rather than try to love and laugh at this loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.66,0:24:03.21,Ending-English,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}I will fight
